title: Rare Hits of The 80s Vol. 23
description:
One more mix of rare 80s songs, possibly the last one. It&#039;s been fun to put these mixes together as it made me go back to many old and forgotten CDs and vinyl records but at the same time a bit time consuming. Anyhow I do hope you enjoyed them and re-discovered some real 80s gems.
